===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Helmholtz coil'''
#{{physics}} one of a pair of flat [[coil]]s, having equal numbers of turns and equal diameters, arranged on a common axis and connected in [[series]]; used to obtain a nearly [[uniform]] [[magnetic field]] without the use of a long [[solenoid]]
